name: Nichibotsu
description:
This work represents the invisible forces that can disrupt a collective organization.
These forces make it possible to create natural and independent movements which nevertheless form a coherent whole.
So although having an apparent freedom of movement the particles are ultimately constrained and there are few that can get out of the frame.

This is the door of the sun which blow the forces in presence.
An original artwork by Noctambul.
